OL,3,CDurham Women FC could 'cease
OL,4,Coperations in three weeks' without
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FDurham Women say they must find fresh
OL,8,Finvestment or a buyer within the next
OL,9,F21 days or the club faces going out of
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FThe club has been in talks with
OL,13,Fpotential investors this year but they
OL,14,Fhave fallen through in recent weeks.
OL,16,FDurham say without investment, they
OL,17,Fwill not have sufficient funds to play
OL,18,Fin the Women's Super League 2 next
OL,19,Fseason and would cease operations at
OL,20,Fall levels.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
