OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780989353
OL,3,CDurham Women FC could 'cease
OL,4,Coperations in three weeks' without
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FIn a statement, the club said: "Durham
OL,8,FWomen Football Club can today confirm
OL,9,Fthat the club is seeking offers for
OL,10,Finvestment into or the complete
OL,11,Fpurchase of the football club.
OL,13,F"The club has been in prolonged talks
OL,14,Fwith potential investors for several
OL,15,Fmonths but these have fallen away in
OL,16,Frecent weeks. Unfortunately, without
OL,17,Fthis additional investment, the club
OL,18,Fdoes not have sufficient funds to
OL,19,Foperate in a fully compliant way in
OL,20,Fthe Barclays Women's Super League 2
OL,21,Ffor the 2026/27 season.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
