FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780989353
OL,3,CDurham Women FC could 'cease
OL,4,Coperations in three weeks' without
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,F"We have today informed staff and
OL,8,Fplayers that unless a buyer or
OL,9,Finvestor comes forward within the next
OL,10,F21 days, the club will have to cease
OL,11,Foperations at all levels."
OL,13,FThe club was first formed in 2007 to
OL,14,Fchampion the development of women's
OL,15,Fand girls' football in the North East.
OL,17,FThey were accepted into the WSL
OL,18,Fstructure in 2014 and were the first
OL,19,Fteam in the region to obtain a licence
OL,20,Ffor a Professional Game Academy with
OL,21,Fteams at junior levels.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
