CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780989353
OL,3,CDurham Women FC could 'cease
OL,4,Coperations in three weeks' without
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FIn their statement, Durham added: "All
OL,8,Fof the above has been achieved without
OL,9,Fthe backing of a men's professional
OL,10,Fteam - but the club's current majority
OL,11,Fshareholders can no longer keep pace
OL,12,Fwith the development of the women's
OL,13,Fgame.
OL,15,F"The club needs to continue - and they
OL,16,Fare now seeking to pass this over to a
OL,17,Fparty who can build on this legacy and
OL,18,Frealise the opportunities that the
OL,19,Fclub has moving forward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
